  <string key="howitworks.kicker">Under the hood</string>
  <string key="howitworks.subtitle">A quick tour.</string>
  <string key="howitworks.apps.title">Apps</string>
  <string key="howitworks.apps.body">Pick the apps that distract you. While a session is running, they'll close automatically if you try to open them.</string>
  <string key="howitworks.websites.title">Websites</string>
  <string key="howitworks.websites.body">Pick domains or use a preset. During the session, your browsers simply can't reach them.</string>
  <string key="howitworks.pomodoro.title">Pomodoro</string>
  <string key="howitworks.pomodoro.body">Run a single focus block or alternate focus and breaks. Blocking is on during focus, off on breaks.</string>
  <string key="howitworks.privacy.title">Privacy</string>
  <string key="howitworks.privacy.body">Everything happens on your Mac. No accounts, no tracking, no data leaves the device.</string>

